Title: An Act Changing the Name of Batu-Bato Emergency Hospital in Bongao, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Datu Halun Sakilan Memorial Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 59
An Act Changing the Name of Batu-Bato Emergency Hospital in Bongao, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Datu Halun Sakilan Memorial Hospital
Section 1. The name of Batu-Bato Emergency Hospital in Bongao, Province of Tawi-Tawi, is hereby changed to Datu Halun Sakilan Memorial Hospital.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1Ã¢wphi1
Approved: March 27, 1980
